# TypeScript / React

- Keep route handlers thin; put logic in `lib/` with collocated tests.
- No `*.test.tsx` under `app/` — use `tests/` for page-level tests.
- Use `@/` imports matching `tsconfig.json` paths.
- Do not add ORM or domain features — this is a reference scaffold.
